    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/f31b3b0de61f0481687809d2cf244e39.avif?t=1770315825\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras_big/f31b3b0de61f0481687809d2cf244e39.avif?t=1770315825 width=800 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Big Band Survivors, you play as a musician battling hordes of strange monsters in 4 different arenas, designed by the alien orchestrators as a gladiatorial spectator sport.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything <strong>adapts dynamically to the music,</strong> changing depending on choices you make in game. In true roguelite fashion,  each run is unique mechanically, but also <strong>unique in its soundscape!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/2e289e55d170f3e24aada96da7b8fd1f.poster.avif?t=1770315825\" width=674 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/2e289e55d170f3e24aada96da7b8fd1f.webm?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/2e289e55d170f3e24aada96da7b8fd1f.mp4?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/8a2ac7051c5a2178d7bc617c67182864.avif?t=1770315825\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras_big/8a2ac7051c5a2178d7bc617c67182864.avif?t=1770315825 width=800 height=56 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the aliens, collect XP, <strong>level up your character</strong>. Doing so will let you upgrade or pick new instruments, improving your odds and attacks, but also <strong>affecting the music </strong>being played.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye out for <strong>care packages</strong> sent by adoring fans as they can give you just what you need in a given moment, but be careful to stay clear of their landing zone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defeat one of the game's <strong>10+ bosses</strong> to be rewarded with a relic, granting strong and often synergistic new abilities to your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/506aca9de7f0143c841e37280d4a8adb.poster.avif?t=1770315825\" width=680 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/506aca9de7f0143c841e37280d4a8adb.webm?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/506aca9de7f0143c841e37280d4a8adb.mp4?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/e2aa461115563df17c9cda17e1779240.avif?t=1770315825\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras_big/e2aa461115563df17c9cda17e1779240.avif?t=1770315825 width=800 height=56 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>After each run, win or lose:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get rewarded with <strong>roses</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend them between runs on powerful <strong>upgrades</strong> to help you survive longer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get closer to earning 47 in-game <strong>achievements</strong> with exciting rewards! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/100d4fe136f5e472e22edcec6ae480f5.poster.avif?t=1770315825\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/100d4fe136f5e472e22edcec6ae480f5.webm?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/100d4fe136f5e472e22edcec6ae480f5.mp4?t=1770315825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">📢Join our <strong>official Discord server!</strong> Get access to dev logs from the team, big game announcements and exciting previews - or just hang with the community! Find the invite link in the <strong>panel to the right,</strong> here on our Steam page😊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/c8252b5db3a688468dee04ddebb92d3a.apng?t=1770315825\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213230/extras/c8252b5db3a688468dee04ddebb92d3a.poster.avif?t=1770315825\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=72 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p>",
